		<title>07Margam Park. Visitor Survey</title>
		<content> Nearly half (45%) of tourist groups   
 stay with friends or relatives.  Only 
 7% stay in hotels or Guest Houses.    
 Only 1 in 20 visitor groups use public
 transport.                            
 Most visitors stayed in Margam Park   
 for between two and three hours.      
 Tourists tended to visit the Park for 
 over three hours.                     
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
